   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"A hero speaks): Therefore, o men, beware and honor us heroes, since we are the givers of bad and good; we punish the rogues, robbers and thieves. To the thieves we give spleen, cough, dropsiness, catarrh, itch, podagra, gout, madness, rash, glandular swelling, cold, fever . . . But to the robbers we give [. . ."</ab>
         </div>
